					<span class="printuser deleted" data-id="3623441"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--images/avatars/default/a16.png" alt=""/>(account deleted)</span> <span class="odate time_1526518408 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">17 May 2018 00:53</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3802795">
									

<p>After all my years of reading the SCP Wiki, this is my first contribution. This is a 049 mpreg fanfiction that was born from a dumb conversation I had with <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(414239); return false;">Gabriel Jade</a></span>. Thanks to <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2303803); return false;">Cyantreuse</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/johnnywannabe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3143180); return false;">JohnnyWannabe</a></span>, and various others from Discord for giving feedback. I was going to wait a bit longer to get more feedback, but I got really nervous and decided to just post it. I'm shaking right now. I really hope this sticks.</p>
<p>Edit: By the way, &quot;Doctor Omel&quot; is short for &quot;Doctor Omelette.&quot; Don't tell anyone.</p>

							</div>

								
